{"tid":1409582,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工已經開始有成效！","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:02:37.000Z","uid":10147,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"202d7fc8c3b7315fa3755c6f782cf8ff8a7cb086","tid":1409582,"uid":10147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8p6vguE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8p6vguE.png&h=0fa9c48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就係響外國翻唔到香港既傻9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但絕對支持大家繼續罷佢老母！<br />\n齊心對抗港共政權 五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"76daf5ffc1fecdfe1a552c71a4909110d649e7f4","tid":1409582,"uid":10147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:45:12.000Z","msg":"推上熱門比大家睇 罷工真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26864036ac493c03db5e264114c0a83db71c37d","tid":1409582,"uid":10147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:45:35.000Z","msg":"只要你肯罷 實有人陪你"},{"pid":"88cda1b6239a4c69b349ab4b6fcfb5907c090fb5","tid":1409582,"uid":10147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:46:59.000Z","msg":"大把同路人 你不孤單"},{"pid":"b8276aeac506b28e1c1fd0e43616b150f3be17e6","tid":1409582,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:51.000Z","msg":"Sudden strike?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0528f642eddb7c4203fc5523c24dd1eeb86d92","tid":1409582,"uid":64463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a36143ab0f3b23ad645d0f459e87cbd548c9ec8","tid":1409582,"uid":134054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:49:09.000Z","msg":"如果俾人插可以咁對答<br />\n➡️阻住我返工<br />\n❌粗口<br />\n⭕️我都好想返工啊<br />\n➡️阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n❌阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n⭕️支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n➡️你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n⭕️係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n⭕️係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n⭕️唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n⭕️林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n⭕️林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n➡️本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n⭕️請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n⭕️其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n⭕️你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會😂<br />\n➡️成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n⭕️今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n⭕️如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n➡️粗口<br />\n❌粗口回應<br />\n⭕️嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅😱<br />\n⭕️嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n⭕️你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n⭕️我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n⭕️我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n⭕️車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"8f5aa252da3d805339ed54ea4bf499506c575228","tid":1409582,"uid":36658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"有幾sudden啊？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1832832aab08751519df704628a18567d4d7f8ae","tid":1409582,"uid":84575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8276aeac506b28e1c1fd0e43616b150f3be17e6","tid":1409582,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:51.000Z","msg":"Sudden strike?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:50:04.000Z","msg":"講左成個禮拜話要罷工架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3c26a71516dc49f645f67edb34c51e9e762bf3","tid":1409582,"uid":10147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8276aeac506b28e1c1fd0e43616b150f3be17e6","tid":1409582,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:51.000Z","msg":"Sudden strike?<img src=\"/a